# {{surfing}} Scraping [[injury]] caused by [[fall]]ing on or being [[drag]]ged over a [[reef]].  (Note this is an actual physical injury, not an [[inflammation]] like a normal [[rash]].)
#: 1999: ''I decided to show the lifeguards my reef rash. "It's just a scratch!" one of them chimed.'' &mdash; Neal Miyake [http://www.hisurfadvisory.com/sesh/new/sesh190.htm]
===Usage note===
It's common to describe even serious injuries caused by a reef as "reef rash", as a form of [[humorous]] or [[macho]] [[understatement]].